<emphasis id="B925EAD2401E5013D7604800FDE2F031" box="[302,517,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">Mahalana lubugris</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D4424800FD44F031" author="Distant, W. L." box="[524,675,259,285]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" refId="ref12320" refString="Distant, W. L. (1918 b) Rhynchota. VII. Homoptera: appendix. Heteroptera: addenda. In: The fauna of British India, including Ceylon and Burma. Taylor &amp; Francis, London, VIII + 210 pp." type="book" year="1918">Distant, 1918</bibRefCitation>
