</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEE36C0401E5013D6D94848FDB3F0A5" blockId="11.[151,1437,331,790]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis id="B925EAD2401E5013D6D94848FF04F049" bold="true" box="[151,227,331,357]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">Notes:</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D43401E5013D724484FFD6CF049" authority="Dlabola, 1981" authorityName="Dlabola" authorityYear="1981" box="[362,651,331,357]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Masiripius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B925EAD2401E5013D724484FFE04F049" box="[362,483,332,357]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">Masiripius</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D7A54848FD6CF049" author="Dlabola, J." box="[491,651,331,357]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" pagination="127 - 308" refId="ref12366" refString="Dlabola, J. (1981 a) Ergebnisse der Tschechoslowakisoh-Iranischen Entomologischen Expedition nach dem Iran. 1970 - 1973). (Mit Angaben uber einige Sammelresultate in Anatolien) Homoptera: Auchenorrhyncha (II. Teil). Acta Entomologica Musie Nationalis Pragae, 40, 127 - 308." type="journal article" year="1981">Dlabola, 1981</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(p. 273) was established with the 
<typeStatus id="54EA8862401E5013D25A484FFBA3F04A" box="[1044,1092,332,358]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">type</typeStatus>
species 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D43401E5013D2E84848FEA4F0A5" authority="Bergevin, 1922" authorityName="Bergevin" authorityYear="1922" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Platymetopius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zizyphi">
<emphasis id="B925EAD2401E5013D2E84848FA7BF049" box="[1190,1436,331,357]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">Platymetopius zizyphi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D6D9486CFEA4F0A5" author="Bergevin, E. de" box="[151,323,367,393]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" pagination="63 - 65" refId="ref10883" refString="Bergevin, E. de. (1922 a) Description d'une nouvelle espece de Platymetopius (hemiptere, homoptere, Jassidae) d'Algerie. Bulletin de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de l'Afrique du Nord, Alger, 13, 63 - 65." type="journal article" year="1922">Bergevin, 1922</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
by original designation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEE36C0401E5013D6894890FBC4F386" blockId="11.[151,1437,331,790]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D6894890FDA6F081" author="Viraktamath, C. A. &amp; Anantha Murthy, H. V." box="[199,577,403,429]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" pagination="39 - 55" refId="ref18878" refString="Viraktamath, C. A. &amp; Anantha Murthy, H. V. (1999 a) A revison [sic] of the leafhopper tribe Scaphytopiini from India and Nepal (Insecta, Hemiptera, Cicadellidae, Deltocephalinae). Senckenbergiana Biologica, 79, 39 - 55." type="journal article" year="1999">Viraktamath &amp; Murthy (1999: 44)</bibRefCitation>
pointed out the misidentification of the 
<typeStatus id="54EA8862401E5013D5B74897FBCEF082" box="[1017,1065,404,430]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D43401E5013D2ED4897FAFBF081" authorityName="Dlabola" authorityYear="1981" box="[1187,1308,404,429]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Masiripius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B925EAD2401E5013D2ED4897FAFBF081" box="[1187,1308,404,429]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">Masiripius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D30A4890FF05F0FD" author="Dlabola, J." pageId="11" pageNumber="36" pagination="127 - 308" refId="ref12366" refString="Dlabola, J. (1981 a) Ergebnisse der Tschechoslowakisoh-Iranischen Entomologischen Expedition nach dem Iran. 1970 - 1973). (Mit Angaben uber einige Sammelresultate in Anatolien) Homoptera: Auchenorrhyncha (II. Teil). Acta Entomologica Musie Nationalis Pragae, 40, 127 - 308." type="journal article" year="1981">Dlabola (1981)</bibRefCitation>
and proposed the actual taxonomic species studied by Dlabola, 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D43401E5013D58548B4FAACF0FD" authority="Distant, 1918" authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1918" box="[971,1355,439,465]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Mahalana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lugubris">
<emphasis id="B925EAD2401E5013D58548B4FB42F0FD" box="[971,1189,439,465]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">Mahalana lugubris</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D2E148B4FAACF0FD" author="Distant, W. L." box="[1199,1355,439,465]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" refId="ref12320" refString="Distant, W. L. (1918 b) Rhynchota. VII. Homoptera: appendix. Heteroptera: addenda. In: The fauna of British India, including Ceylon and Burma. Taylor &amp; Francis, London, VIII + 210 pp." type="book" year="1918">Distant, 1918</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, as the new 
<typeStatus id="54EA8862401E5013D68048DFFF19F0DA" box="[206,254,476,502]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">type</typeStatus>
species of the genus. Unfortunately, according to the 3rd edition of the International Code of Zoological Nomenclature (
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D70848FCFE34F336" author="ICZN" box="[326,467,511,538]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" refId="ref14934" refString="ICZN (1985) International Code of Zoological Nomenclature. 3 rd Edition. The International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London, xx + 338 pp." type="book" year="1985">ICZN, 1985</bibRefCitation>
), effective at that time, this was an illegitimate action. The cases of 
<typeStatus id="54EA8862401E5013D2974B03FAEEF336" box="[1241,1289,512,538]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">type</typeStatus>
species misidentification (Article 70b) had to be referred to the Commission for resolution. The 4th edition of the International Code of Zoological Nomenclature (
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D4694B44FD55F34D" author="ICZN &amp; London, XXIX" box="[551,690,583,609]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" refId="ref14962" refString="ICZN (1999) International Code of Zoological Nomenclature. 4 th edition. The International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London, XXIX + 306 pp." type="book" year="1999">ICZN, 1999</bibRefCitation>
) allows resolution of the cases like this one without application to the Commission. Article 70.3.2 is applied here to fix 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D43401E5013D4A84B68FBBAF3A9" authority="Distant, 1918" authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1918" box="[742,1117,619,645]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Mahalana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lubugris">
<emphasis id="B925EAD2401E5013D4A84B68FC5BF3A9" box="[742,956,619,645]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">Mahalana lubugris</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D58D4B68FBBAF3A9" author="Distant, W. L." box="[963,1117,619,645]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" refId="ref12320" refString="Distant, W. L. (1918 b) Rhynchota. VII. Homoptera: appendix. Heteroptera: addenda. In: The fauna of British India, including Ceylon and Burma. Taylor &amp; Francis, London, VIII + 210 pp." type="book" year="1918">Distant, 1918</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, the taxonomic species actually involved in the misidentification as the 
<typeStatus id="54EA8862401E5013D4CA4B93FD53F386" box="[644,692,656,682]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">type</typeStatus>
species of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D43401E5013D5EC4B93FBFCF385" authorityName="Dlabola" authorityYear="1981" box="[930,1051,656,681]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Masiripius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B925EAD2401E5013D5EC4B93FBFCF385" box="[930,1051,656,681]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">Masiripius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEE36C0401E5013D6894BB0FE14F23A" blockId="11.[151,1437,331,790]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">
This action preserves the genus 
<emphasis id="B925EAD2401E5013D4744BB0FD27F3E1" box="[570,704,691,717]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">Oshaibahus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D4874BB0FBE5F3E1" author="El-Sonbati, S. A. &amp; Wilson, M. R. &amp; Al Dhafer, H. M." box="[713,1026,691,717]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" pagination="1 - 24" refId="ref12997" refString="El-Sonbati, S. A., Wilson, M. R. &amp; Al Dhafer, H. M. (2017 a) A new leafhopper genus with two new species related to Masiripius Dlabola, 1981 (Hemiptera, Deltocephalinae, Cicadellidae, Opsiini). European Journal of Taxonomy, 308, 1 - 24. https: // doi. org / 10.5852 / ejt. 2017.308" type="journal article" year="2017">
El-Sonbati &amp; Wilson, 
<quantity id="4CA99B25401E5013D5844BB0FBE5F3E1" box="[970,1026,691,717]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.12318" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" unit="in" value="2017.0">2017</quantity>
</bibRefCitation>
in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D2644BB0FEE8F3DD" author="El-Sonbati, S. A. &amp; Wilson, M. R. &amp; Al Dhafer, H. M." pageId="11" pageNumber="36" pagination="1 - 24" refId="ref12997" refString="El-Sonbati, S. A., Wilson, M. R. &amp; Al Dhafer, H. M. (2017 a) A new leafhopper genus with two new species related to Masiripius Dlabola, 1981 (Hemiptera, Deltocephalinae, Cicadellidae, Opsiini). European Journal of Taxonomy, 308, 1 - 24. https: // doi. org / 10.5852 / ejt. 2017.308" type="journal article" year="2017">El-Sonbati, Wilson &amp; Al Dhafer (2017: 10)</bibRefCitation>
as valid because the latter was established based on the 
<typeStatus id="54EA8862401E5013D5D24BDBFC2BF3DE" box="[924,972,728,754]" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">type</typeStatus>
species 
<taxonomicName id="4C514D43401E5013D2614BD4FF28F239" authority="Bergevin, 1922" authorityName="Bergevin" authorityYear="1922" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Platymetopius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zizyphi">
<emphasis id="B925EAD2401E5013D2614BD4FAC1F3DD" box="[1071,1318,727,753]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="36">Platymetopius zizyphi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC04B31401E5013D3614BD4FF28F239" author="Bergevin, E. de" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" pagination="63 - 65" refId="ref10883" refString="Bergevin, E. de. (1922 a) Description d'une nouvelle espece de Platymetopius (hemiptere, homoptere, Jassidae) d'Algerie. Bulletin de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de l'Afrique du Nord, Alger, 13, 63 - 65." type="journal article" year="1922">Bergevin, 1922</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(by original designation).
</paragraph>
